{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"75eb36d65b","title":"中共中央转发华东局关于农村债务纠纷处理办法给中南局的电报","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b84ec9ac29","index":0,"year":1950,"month":8,"day":25,"articleId":"75eb36d65b"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9532db6c0d","type":"title","text":"中共中央转发华东局关于农村债务纠纷处理办法给中南局的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"0796e0f5f4","type":"appellation","text":"中南局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"f8a4939ecd","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将华东局拟就之农村债务纠纷处理办法转给你们，望你们参考并同样拟就一个办法电告。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"4fce3aa17e","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央八月二十五日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"b9fdce64b4","type":"appellation","text":"中央：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"3e7fd5b2de","type":"paragraph","text":"遵照午删电示精神，拟就华东区农村债务纠纷处理暂行办法草案一件，呈阅批核，原文如下：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"c292eac0a9","type":"paragraph","text":"废除解放前封建的高利贷债务及保障解放后农村人民借贷自由，乃我人民政府之既定政策。在今后土地改革中，农村人民在清理过去债务时，可能发生若干纠纷。为合理地处理解放以前的债务纠纷，以利生产起见，特订定下列暂行办法。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"d7755c3e06","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）解放前农民及其他劳动人民所欠地主的债务，一律废除。解放前其他债务继续有效，如发生纠纷，由政府按照下列原则调处之：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"281f69e289","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、农民所欠富农的债务，利倍本（即借本百元已付利息百元者）停利还本，利二倍于本（即借本百元已付利息二百元者）本利停付。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"2c7164a2f2","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、农民所欠农民的债务，由双方协议处理。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"b05ada1d9d","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、凡货物买卖及工商业往来欠账，仍依双方原约定处理。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"7f3c21fca6","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）解放后一切债务由双方自愿约定之，利息均继续有效，包括地主出借的在内。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"f34666af2b","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）今后借贷自由，利息由双方议定，政府不加干涉。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"a87d41569d","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）本办法自公布之日起施行，解释权属于华东军政委员会，其修改权亦同。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"},{"id":"79d7085df4","type":"paragraph","text":" 华东局未  删","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b"}],"page":{"id":"19876617f2","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"75eb36d65b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}